{"data":[{"date":"14:38 13/11","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i coi \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i nguy hi\u1ec3m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u1edf AFF Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/12/nguoi-thai-coi-dt-viet-nam-la-moi-nguy-hiem-lon-nhat-o-aff-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan Somyot Poompanmoung \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i nguy hi\u1ec3m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u1edf AFF Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i coi tr\u1ecdng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam&nbsp;\u1edf AFF Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i AFF Cup 2018. Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0110\u00f4ng Timor t\u1edbi 7-0, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 trong tay nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo, ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111ang b\u1ecb lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Somyot coi tr\u1ecdng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf AFF Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Somyot coi tr\u1ecdng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf AFF Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/Chu-tich-Somyot-coi-trong-DT-Viet-Nam-o-AFF-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Somyot coi tr\u1ecdng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf AFF Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan, \u00f4ng Somyot c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y: &ldquo;\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch&nbsp;AFF Cup, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u L\u0110B\u0110 x\u1ee9 ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3 Malaysia, Philippines, Indonesia v\u00e0 Singapore \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i l\u1edbn tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Rajevac.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Somyot Poompanmoung v\u1eabn tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u1edf k\u1ef3 AFF Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nh\u1edb nh\u1eefng Chanathip, Dangda, Theerathon v\u00e0 Kawin. Song, 'Voi chi\u1ebfn' \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. T\u00f4i tin \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 ra&quot;, \u00f4ng Somyot cho bi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/aff-cup-c334-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">AFF Cup</span> n\u0103m nay g\u1eb7p \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 17/11.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&#10;\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/aff-cup-2018/sao-thai-lan-sang-nhat-ban-thi-dau-sau-aff-cup-2018-334-202109.html\">Sao Th\u00e1i Lan sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n thi \u0111\u1ea5u sau AFF Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/aff-cup-2018/hlv-thai-lan-tiet-lo-ly-do-thang-huy-diet-timor-leste-o-ngay-ra-quan-aff-cup-334-201938.html\">HLV Th\u00e1i Lan ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do th\u1eafng h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Timor Leste \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n AFF Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/clb-thai-lan-muon-chieu-mo-thu-mon-dang-van-lam-sau-aff-cup-2018-168-201925.html\">CLB Th\u00e1i Lan mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m sau AFF Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/aff-cup-2018/ngoi-sao-thai-lan-ghi-6-ban-o-tran-thang-timor-leste-tung-muon-giai-nghe-334-201909.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Th\u00e1i Lan ghi 6 b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Timor Leste t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/aff-cup-2018/tien-dao-thai-lan-di-vao-lich-su-aff-cup-sau-tran-dai-thang-dong-timor-334-201857.html\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed AFF Cup sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng \u0110\u00f4ng Timor</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-timor-leste-07-thai-lan-bang-b-aff-cup-2018-482-201849.html\">Video: Timor Leste 0-7 Th\u00e1i Lan (B\u1ea3ng B AFF Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"9389","checkdouble":"202170"},{"date":"15:06 13/11","title":"Tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng HLV Park Hang Seo l\u1ecdt top 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t AFF Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/8/anh-duc-lot-top-5-cau-thu-an-tuong-nhat-aff-cup-2018.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trang th\u1ec3 thao qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf Fox Sports Asia m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 li\u1ec7t k\u00ea ra 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng AFF Cup 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>Anh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ecdt top 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t AFF Cup 2018\u00a0</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng AFF Cup 2018, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb \u0110T Singapore b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Indonesia th\u00ec \u1edf 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Malaysia v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc L\u00e0o, Campuchia v\u00e0 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ecdt top 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t AFF Cup 2018  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Anh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ecdt top 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t AFF Cup 2018  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/8/Anh-Duc-lot-top-5-cau-thu-an-tuong-nhat-AFF-Cup-2018--hinh-anh.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Anh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ecdt top 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t AFF Cup 2018\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 trang th\u1ec3 thao qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf Fox Sports Asia m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 li\u1ec7t k\u00ea ra 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u00e0y. C\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 Fox Sports Asia \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Adisak Kraisorn c\u1ee7a \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110\u00f4ng Timor th\u00e0nh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh khi ghi t\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Adisak, Fox Sport c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c. Trang b\u00e1o n\u00e0y m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: \u201cL\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng Anh \u0110\u1ee9c lu\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft, c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00f3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1eadp \u00fd ch\u00ed chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 tri\u1ec7u voi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf h\u1eefu chi\u1ec1u cao l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng 1m82 c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Fox Sports vinh danh l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Zaquan Adha (Malaysia), Zulqarnaen Suzliman (Singapore) v\u00e0 Chan Vathanaka (Campuchia)..<span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"9388","checkdouble":"202174"},{"date":"15:36 13/11","title":"T\u00e2n binh \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u00f3t tay c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/13/tan-binh-dt-viet-nam-co-ben-do-moi-voi-muc-lot-tay-khung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>S\u00e1ng 13/11, t\u00e2n binh \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u2013 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110inh Vi\u1ebft T\u00fa \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh sau 14 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00f3t tay kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110inh Vi\u1ebft T\u00fa c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u00f3t tay kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p>\u0110inh Vi\u1ebft T\u00fa l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 5 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo g\u1ecdi l\u00ean \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/aff-cup-c334-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">AFF Cup 2018</span>. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i song vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n l\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ch\u00e0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110inh Vi\u1ebft T\u00fa c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u00f3t tay kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110inh Vi\u1ebft T\u00fa c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u00f3t tay kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/10/8/Hau-ve-Dinh-Viet-Tu-co-ben-do-moi-voi-muc-lot-tay-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110inh Vi\u1ebft T\u00fa (gi\u1eefa) chia tay Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh sau V-League 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Vi\u1ebft T\u00fa \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong mi\u1ec1n Nam \u1edf V-League 2019. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: &quot;14 n\u0103m tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng th\u0103ng tr\u1ea7m ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t.&nbsp;<strongr noto=\"\">Kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t. C\u00e1m \u01a1n c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ean t\u00f4i \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh.&nbsp;<strongr>M\u1ed9t l\u1eddi c\u00e1m \u01a1n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ee7 v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9&quot;.<o:p></o:p></strongr></strongr></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i, t\u00e2n binh \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi b\u00e1o ch\u00ed: &quot;\u0110\u1eddi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p kh\u00f4ng d\u00e0i v\u00e0 t\u00f4i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec3 lo \u0111\u1ee7 kinh t\u1ebf cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng theo Vi\u1ebft T\u00fa, \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi anh c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ee3 con v\u00e0o Nam sinh s\u1ed1ng: &quot;T\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00f3t tay l\u00e0&nbsp;3 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng/3 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, l\u01b0\u01a1ng 35 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng/th\u00e1ng&quot;, Vi\u1ebft T\u00fa ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110inh Vi\u1ebft T\u00fa l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam \u1edf V-League 2018 v\u00e0 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n c\u00f9ng CLB n\u00e0y tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng Vi\u1ebft T\u00fa, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf anh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&#10;\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tan-binh-dt-viet-nam-tho-phao-vi-doi-nha-tru-hang-thanh-cong-168-199434.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/10/8/tan-binh-dt-viet-nam-tho-phao-vi-doi-nha-tru-hang-thanh-cong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tan-binh-dt-viet-nam-tho-phao-vi-doi-nha-tru-hang-thanh-cong-168-199434.html\">T\u00e2n binh \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1edd ph\u00e0o v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0110inh Vi\u1ebft T\u00fa th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/nam-dinh-vs-ha-noi-b-vleague-2018-372-199412.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/10/13/nam-dinh-vs-ha-noi-b-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/nam-dinh-vs-ha-noi-b-vleague-2018-372-199412.html\">Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh 0-0 (pen 5-3) H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i B (KT): Th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i V-League</span><br>\r\nB\u1ecf l\u1ee1 v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n trong th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e0nh ph\u1ea3i k\u00e9o \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m \u1edf tr\u1eadn playoff tranh su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"9387","checkdouble":"202183"},{"date":"16:38 13/11","title":"C\u00f4ng Vinh m\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ea1 Malaysia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/cong-vinh-mach-nuoc-de-dt-viet-nam-ha-malaysia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam L\u00ea C\u00f4ng Vinh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Malaysia.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 16.5pt;\"><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\" style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: start;\">C\u00f4ng Vinh m\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ea1 Malaysia</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: start;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mot nam duoi thoi Quyen chu tich Le Cong Vinh, CLB TP.HCM da co nhieu thay doi tich cuc. Anh: Tung Le/Zing.vn\" title=\"M\u1ed9t n\u0103m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Quy\u1ec1n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch L\u00ea C\u00f4ng Vinh, CLB TP.HCM \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. \u1ea2nh: T\u00f9ng L\u00ea/Zing.vn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/cong-vinh-mach-nuoc-de-dt-viet-nam-ha-malaysia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00f4ng Vinh tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd h\u1ea1 Malaysia. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Malaysia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u chung k\u1ebft s\u1edbm t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/aff-cup-c334-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">AFF Cup 2018</span>. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u1eabn l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean Malaysia ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o L\u00ea C\u00f4ng Vinh \u0111\u00e3 m\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo &lsquo;h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i&rsquo; \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Malaysia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1t&rdquo;, C\u00f4ng Vinh t\u00e2m s\u1ef1. &ldquo;N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi Malaysia, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n kho\u00e1 ch\u1eb7t 2 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 bi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i v\u1edbi g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb Akhyar Rashid r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Malaysia l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 h\u1ecd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o c\u1ef1u binh Talaha&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 ra c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Malaysia, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o L\u00ea C\u00f4ng Vinh c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo. Danh th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;T\u00f4i tin ch\u1eafc n\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang phong \u0111\u1ed9, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y hai n\u0103m, C\u00f4ng Vinh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Malaysia \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0 nh\u1edd pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch khi b\u1ecb Indonesia lo\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.5pt; text-align: justify;\"><em><u>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n</u></em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/aff-cup-2018/anh-duc-lot-top-5-cau-thu-an-tuong-nhat-aff-cup-2018-334-202174.html\">Tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng HLV Park Hang Seo l\u1ecdt top 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t AFF Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/aff-cup-2018/nguoi-thai-coi-dt-viet-nam-la-moi-nguy-hiem-lon-nhat-o-aff-cup-2018-334-202170.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i coi \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i nguy hi\u1ec3m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u1edf AFF Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/day-thong-ke-dang-mung-cho-dt-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-malaysia-292-202164.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng cho \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Malaysia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thuyen-truong-malaysia-khang-dinh-se-choi-tan-cong-truoc-viet-nam-168-202162.html\">Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Malaysia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tan-binh-dt-viet-nam-co-ben-do-moi-voi-muc-lot-tay-khung-168-202183.html\">T\u00e2n binh \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u00f3t tay c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"9386","checkdouble":"202193"},{"date":"18:00 13/11","title":"\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea5u Malaysia: \u0110\u00e1 ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u hay ru ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/11/13/dt-viet-nam-dau-malaysia-da-phu-dau-hay-ru-ngu-doi-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa, tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Malaysia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m?</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 16.5pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ea7y Park v\u00e0 b\u00e0i to\u00e1n h\u1ea1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u00e3<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 16/11 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chung k\u1ebft s\u1edbm t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A gi\u1eefa \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Malaysia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean SV\u0110 qu\u1ed1c gia M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 song c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u01a1 l\u00e0, khi m\u00e0 \u0110T Malaysia lu\u00f4n nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang ta &lsquo;\u00f4m h\u1eadn&rsquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, t\u1ea1i AFF Cup 2014, ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u00e3 t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-2 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Toshiya Miura khi \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Malaysia \u0110\u00e1 ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u hay ru ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Malaysia \u0110\u00e1 ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u hay ru ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/2/DT-Viet-Nam-vs-Malaysia-Da-phu-dau-hay-ru-ngu-doi-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eebng nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia t\u1ea1i AFF Cup n\u0103m 2014.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i tranh ch\u1ea5p, \u0110T Malaysia lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 li\u1ec7u ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1edd l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 hay \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f2 c\u01b0a, ru ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n th\u00f4i, c\u1ee9 x\u1ebfp m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p L\u00e0o, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 hai v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 lo ng\u1ea1i l\u00e0 li\u1ec7u tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u1edbi Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Quang H\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng &lsquo;m\u00e1y qu\u00e9t&rsquo; gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Malaysia v\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba c\u00e1c \u0111\u00f2n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng 'h\u1ed3i m\u00e3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng' c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-ban-thang-viet-nam-24-malaysia-ban-ket-aff-cup-2014-325-100664.html\">Video b\u00e0n th\u1eafng: Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-4 Malaysia (B\u00e1n k\u1ebft AFF Cup 2014)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: normal;\">D\u0129 nhi\u00ean khi tri\u1ec3n khai m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u00e2ng cao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t sinh nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t c\u1eadp n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o: <em>&quot;\u0110\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f3 l\u00ean b\u00f3ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sai l\u1ea7m n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfng. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, khi &quot;qu\u00e2y&quot; \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u00ec ph\u00eda sau l\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u1ed9 ra nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n&quot;.<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/11/hlv-le-thuy-hai-lo-ngai-cho-dt-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-malaysia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111ang \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea5u Malaysia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Do v\u1eady n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 b\u1edfi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Malaysia t\u1eebng cho th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf Asiad n\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1 &lsquo;c\u00f2 c\u01b0a&rsquo; ch\u1edd c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd an to\u00e0n h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhau t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0m xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: normal;\">S\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i tr\u0103n tr\u1edf c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/aff-cup-c334-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">AFF Cup 2018</span>. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p L\u00e0o, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam&nbsp;ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 50/50. V\u00ec v\u1eady, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p phung ph\u00ed s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u00edt \u1ecfi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea5u Malaysia?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 an to\u00e0n khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Malaysia thay v\u00ec c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi L\u00e0o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1. \u1ede v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng s\u1ebd v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Khi \u1ea5y su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh DTVN\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110TVN\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/lineup.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn&nbsp;Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Malaysia&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1ed9 ba Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean V\u0103n H\u1eadu v\u00e0 Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng. \u1ede tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u1ea9y Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00ean cao \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1nh h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eafm. Su\u1ea5t c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ho\u1eb7c C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Malaysia l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f9ng V\u0103n To\u00e0n ho\u1eb7c Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c trong hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn. Khi \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/doi-tuyen-viet-nam-c292-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam </span>s\u1ebd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhanh nh\u1eb9n, c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Malaysia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y 16/11 tr\u00ean SV\u0110 M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh. Bongda24h s\u1ebd c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c n\u00e0y. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/11/8/Lao-0-3-Viet-Nam.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><u>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:</u></em></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/day-thong-ke-dang-mung-cho-dt-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-malaysia-292-202164.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/8/day-thong-ke-dang-mung-cho-dt-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/day-thong-ke-dang-mung-cho-dt-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-malaysia-292-202164.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng cho \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Malaysia</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi Malaysia v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 16/11 t\u1edbi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m y\u00ean t\u00e2m khi bi\u1ebft th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y: \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i SV\u0110 M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-vinh-mach-nuoc-de-dt-viet-nam-ha-malaysia-168-202193.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/cong-vinh-mach-nuoc-de-dt-viet-nam-ha-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-vinh-mach-nuoc-de-dt-viet-nam-ha-malaysia-168-202193.html\">C\u00f4ng Vinh m\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ea1 Malaysia</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam L\u00ea C\u00f4ng Vinh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Malaysia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thuyen-truong-malaysia-khang-dinh-se-choi-tan-cong-truoc-viet-nam-168-202162.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/13/thuyen-truong-malaysia-khang-dinh-se-choi-tan-cong-truoc-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thuyen-truong-malaysia-khang-dinh-se-choi-tan-cong-truoc-viet-nam-168-202162.html\">Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Malaysia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nS\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 16/11 t\u1edbi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean r\u1ea5t cao, khi HLV Malaysia tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.5pt; text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"9385","checkdouble":"202195"},{"date":"17:50 13/11","title":"4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn Bayern Munich kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/11/13/4-cau-thu-khien-bayern-munich-khoi-dau-te-hai.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bayern Munich kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, h\u1ecd \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 \u1edf Bundesliga v\u00e0 k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng Dortmund t\u1edbi 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2>Manuel Neuer</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nManuel Neuer t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c. Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n, Neuer kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn Bayern Munich kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn Bayern Munich kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/4-cau-thu-khien-Bayern-Munich-khoi-dau-te-hai-o-mua-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Manuel Neuer</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a n\u00e0y anh c\u0169ng g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t tr\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bayern Munich. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1, ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed hay ra v\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Neuer \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn thua 2-3 c\u1ee7a Bayern tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dortmund m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Manuel Neuer l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Bayern Munich kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2016/17, Neuer ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 0.5 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn, m\u00f9a n\u00e0y anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 14 b\u00e0n thua sau 11 tr\u1eadn (1,27 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn). C\u0169ng \u1edf m\u00f9a 2016/17, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 c\u00f3 1,9 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1/tr\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y con s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 1,1 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn. Trong s\u1ed1 18 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ra s\u00e2n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 5 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Bundesliga m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Manuel Neuer \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 17 v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n c\u1ee9u thua/tr\u1eadn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nFranck ribery</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFranck Ribery \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 11 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Bayern Munich, trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1983 \u0111ang g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Franck Ribery gop dau giay trong ca 2 ban thang cua Bayern truoc Sevilla\" title=\"Franck Ribery g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Bayern tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-dau-Sevilla-vs-Bayern-Munich---Tu-ket-C1-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Franck Ribery</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 14 l\u1ea7n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 961 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng anh ch\u01b0a g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 35, Ribery \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111ua t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o hay d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng suy gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, trung b\u00ecnh Ribery t\u1ea1o ra 2.5 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i/90 ph\u00fat cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf Bundesliga, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 1.6/90 ph\u00fat. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng gi\u1ea3m t\u1eeb 3.7 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 1.6 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u0103ng l\u00ean (2.2 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y so v\u1edbi 1.5 \u1edf m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc) nh\u01b0ng Ribery v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o sau 9 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Bundesliga. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 35 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV Kovac. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern, Uli Hoeness, \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea3i t\u1ed5 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ribery s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMats Hummels</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Mats Hummels ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c. Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern Munich, anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Trong tr\u1eadn thua 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dortmund, Hummels li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Marco Reus v\u00e0 Paco Alcacer ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mats Hummels\" title=\"Mats Hummels\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/hum.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mats Hummels</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Hummels \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc 2 l\u1ed7i ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua, nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo;. Ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c c\u1ef1u sao Dortmund kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Neuer li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Hummels \u0111\u1ec1u suy gi\u1ea3m r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1.6 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, th\u1ea5p con con s\u1ed1 2.3 l\u1ea7n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18. T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng (1.3 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y) c\u0169ng suy gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 (m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 2.1 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat).</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nThomas Muller</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Thomas Muller ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, anh c\u00f3 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 14 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf Bundesliga. Tuy nhi\u00ean, giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ra s\u00e2n 14 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Bundesliga v\u00e0 Champions League nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 ghi 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thomas Muller\" title=\"Thomas Muller\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/miller.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thomas Muller</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, trong 739 ph\u00fat g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 anh g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Bayern \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n 2 th\u00e1ng (01/09).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThomas Muller c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Kovac v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh.&nbsp;M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 29 tu\u1ed5i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 1.9 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, m\u00f9a n\u00e0y th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 1.7. S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng gi\u1ea3m t\u1eeb 2.7 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat xu\u1ed1ng 1.7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMuller c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/bayern-munich-1567.html\" target=\"_blank\"><em><u>Bayern Munich</u></em></span> \u1edf Bundesliga m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Trung b\u00ecnh anh ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 45 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n duy nh\u1ea5t Robert Lewandowski (32).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"9384","checkdouble":"202197"},{"date":"15:12 13/11","title":"Barca l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ee5c n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9: Suarez h\u1eb1m h\u00e8 Pique sau tr\u1eadn thua Betis","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/13/barca-luc-duc-noi-bo-suarez-ham-he-pique-sau-tran-thua-betis.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Hai ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i gay g\u1eaft khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i s\u1ed1c ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Camp Nou.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Pique v\u00e0 Suarez c\u00e3i nhau sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i s\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br>\r\nLionel Messi t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t s\u00e2n c\u1ecf sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Real Betis. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng cho Barcelona c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/barca-vs-betis-la-liga-11112018-372-202008.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 3-4</span> ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Camp Nou.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pique v\u00e0 Suarez c\u00e3i nhau tr\u1eadn Barca thua Betis h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pique v\u00e0 Suarez c\u00e3i nhau tr\u1eadn Barca thua Betis h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/6082820-0-image-a-32_1542024094973.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Pique v\u00e0 Suarez c\u00e3i nhau tr\u1eadn Barca thua Betis</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c n\u00e0y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o g\u00e2y l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ee5c n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 Barca khi Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Gerard Pique \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i n\u1ea3y l\u1eeda sau \u0111\u00f3. Theo c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia ph\u00e2n t\u00edch kh\u1ea9u h\u00ecnh, Suarez \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng gay g\u1eaft sau khi nghe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb Pique: &quot;Gi\u1edd c\u1eadu t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t v\u1ea5n t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea5y \u00e0? \u0110\u1eebng c\u00f3 gi\u1ee1n m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi t\u00f4i!&quot;</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m to chuy\u1ec7n, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t b\u00e0n d\u00e2n thi\u00ean h\u1ea1 l\u00fac b\u1ea5y gi\u1edd khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111ang tr\u00ean ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ea7m, Pique nh\u1eabn nh\u1ecbn xua tay, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng m\u1eb7t ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng l\u00f2ng: &quot;Ok, th\u00edch th\u00ec c\u1ee9 cho l\u00e0 v\u1eady \u0111i.&quot;</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nBarca v\u1eabn b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u La Liga, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t n\u00e0y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd b\u1ecb nh\u00f3m b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng Sevilla, Atletico Madrid, Alaves hay Espanyol v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1-2 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n ki\u1ebfp Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb xem nh\u1eb9 trong m\u1ecdi ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 6.</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 hai tu\u1ea7n nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia, Barca s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Atletico Madrid. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Vicente Calderon s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 2h45 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt 25/11, gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/messi-tro-lai-va-barca-tham-bai-vi-dau-nen-noi-180-202051.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/12/messi-tro-lai-va-barca-tham-bai-vi-dau-nen-noi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/messi-tro-lai-va-barca-tham-bai-vi-dau-nen-noi-180-202051.html\">Messi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 Barca th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i: V\u00ec \u0111\u00e2u n\u00ean n\u1ed7i?</span><br>\r\nBarcelona ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Lionel Messi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ai ng\u1edd h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i thua th\u1ea3m Real Betis 3-4 ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. D\u01b0 \u00e2m Barca 3-4 Betis ch\u1ec9 ra nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-barca-dung-thay-trang-vang-vac-ma-tuong-troi-da-sang-180-202156.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/12/goc-barca-dung-thay-trang-vang-vac-ma-tuong-troi-da-sang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-barca-dung-thay-trang-vang-vac-ma-tuong-troi-da-sang-180-202156.html\">G\u00f3c Barca: \u0110\u1eebng th\u1ea5y tr\u0103ng v\u1eb1ng v\u1eb7c m\u00e0 t\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 s\u00e1ng!</span><br>\r\n4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua, th\u1eafng h\u00f2a thua \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 song c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m chung: Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Barca kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t ch\u00fat n\u00e0o. Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid, d\u01b0\u1eddng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)&nbsp;</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"9383","checkdouble":"202180"},{"date":"16:52 13/11","title":"\u201cVua Panenka\u201d l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i Sergio Ramos","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/11/13/antonin-panenka-phat-bieu-ve-sergio-ramos.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Antonin Panenka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sergio Ramos. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi khai s\u00e1ng ra ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 penalty n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch thu\u1ea7n th\u1ee5c.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Panenka khai s\u00e1ng ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 penalty</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAntonin Panenka t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Ti\u1ec7p Kh\u1eafc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u0103m 1973 t\u1edbi 1982. C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng sinh n\u0103m 1948 nay l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB Bohemians Praha, n\u01a1i \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m. Trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Panenka \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 penalty \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Euro 1976 v\u1edbi T\u00e2y \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Belgrade.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m, Panenka c\u00f3 c\u00fa b\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa khung th\u00e0nh khi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng Sepp Maier \u0111\u00e3 bay v\u1ec1 b\u00ean tr\u00e1i. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 penalty c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ti\u1ec7p Kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi sao ch\u00e9p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Antonin Panenka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sergio Ramos v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Antonin Panenka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sergio Ramos v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/antonin-panenka-phat-bieu-ve-sergio-ramos.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ramos th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 Panenka</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKhen ng\u1ee3i Ramos</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n penalty ki\u1ec3u Panenka n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Sergio Ramos. M\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Celta Vigo v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 penalty ki\u1ec3u Panenka c\u1ee7a Ramos tr\u01b0\u1edbc Celta:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/11/12/real-83.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\nAntonin Panenka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sergio Ramos tr\u00ean t\u1edd AS. Ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i 69 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0m. \u201c<em>T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Ramos th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n penalty theo phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u n\u00f3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady</em>\u201d, Panenka chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>N\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i nh\u1edb l\u1ea1i k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m t\u1eeb Belgrade n\u0103m 1976. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u1edbn l\u1ea1nh! T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o r\u1eb1ng Ramos \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ed9t ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u danh th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>Ramos ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng. T\u00f4i nh\u1edb nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>C\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Celta l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 Panenka th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t t\u00f4i t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y \u1edf Ramos. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t th\u00edch v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao n\u00f3. M\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, kh\u00f4ng nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec n\u1eefa.</em>\u201d <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-viktoria-plzen-05-real-madrid-cuoc-hon-phoi-tot-dep-giua-184-201686.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/8/thang-lon-sao-real-muon-hlv-tam-quyen-o-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-viktoria-plzen-05-real-madrid-cuoc-hon-phoi-tot-dep-giua-184-201686.html\">Real Madrid l\u1ea1i th\u1eafng: Cu\u1ed9c h\u00f4n ph\u1ed1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p gi\u1eefa Viking v\u00e0 \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9</span><br>\r\n<span>Real Madrid th\u1eddi Santiago Solari v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Viktoria Plzen \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 3.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/celta-vigo-vs-real-madrid-vong-12-la-liga-201819-hom-nay-372-202027.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/10/celta-vigo-vs-real-madrid-vong-12-la-liga-201819-hom-nay.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/celta-vigo-vs-real-madrid-vong-12-la-liga-201819-hom-nay-372-202027.html\">Celta 2-4 Real Madrid (KT): Tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n Solari kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng</span><br>\r\n<span>HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n Solari ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Real khi c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec m\u1ea1ch chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Celta \u1edf v\u00f2ng...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"9382","checkdouble":"202191"},{"date":"15:54 13/11","title":"C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a MU th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Matic","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/6/cac-ngoi-sao-cua-mu-that-vong-voi-matic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Nemanja Matic, theo t\u1edd Times, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.\r\n</h2><h2>Matic ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Man City, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 M.U \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 5 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, 3 l\u1ea7n trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. C\u1ea3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n v\u00e0 De Gea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Nemanja Matic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Nemanja Matic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/6/cac-ngoi-sao-cua-mu-that-vong-voi-matic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Matic ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 M.U d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n b\u1edfi Nemanja Matic kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n t\u1eeb xa. \u1ede b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-1 c\u1ee7a Ilkay Gundogan, ch\u00ednh Matic l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng theo k\u00e8m ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 anh d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City, trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Matic ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a anh khi\u1ebfn Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n thua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a M.U kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Matic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMU m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Nemanja Matic, theo t\u1edd Times, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Matic choi that vong truoc Juventus\" title=\"Matic ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/10/24/matic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a MU th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Matic&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Matic li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng khi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n Mourinho \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1ef1u sao Chelsea l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n cho t\u00e2n binh Fred.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Matic \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 m\u1eb7t t\u00e2m l\u00fd, \u0111\u1ec3 anh ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi thi \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n khi c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG, M.U s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Crystal Palace. Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Top 4 \u0111ang l\u00e0 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m, b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/pogba-va-martial-bat-ngo-rut-khoi-dt-phap-184-202131.html\" target=\"_blank\"><em><u>Martial v\u00e0 Pogba \u0111ang d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</u></em></span>, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Palace v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 24/11 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"9381","checkdouble":"202182"},{"date":"15:44 13/11","title":"Sao Liverpool t\u1ef1 tin Man City s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n s\u1ebd s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/10/18/sao-liverpool-tu-tin-man-city-som-muon-se-say-chan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Virgil Van Dijk v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch cam go hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u1edf Premier League.</h2><div>C\u1ea3m \u01a1n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/du-am-tran-hoa-chelsea-vs-everton-172-202069.html\" target=\"_blank\">ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Everton \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n Chelsea</span> ngay tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch Stamford Bridge, Liverpool v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec Premier League sau v\u00f2ng 12 cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jurgen Klopp v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ng\u1eafn kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Man City.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Van Dijk c\u1ee7a Liverpool th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Van Dijk c\u1ee7a Liverpool th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/10/18/goc-nhin-virgil-van-dijk-chien-binh-nam-giu-van-menh-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Trung v\u1ec7 Van Dijk c\u1ee7a Liverpool th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nV\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u Premier League \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau g\u1ea7n 30 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 \u0111a s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t so v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 t\u00e2n v\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 hai \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 san b\u1eb1ng tr\u00ean BXH.</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng sao h\u1ebft, trung v\u1ec7 Virgil Van Dijk v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n g\u00ec Man City c\u0169ng s\u1ebd s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u1eddi c\u01a1 b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi: <em>&quot;H\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a h\u1ecd b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 chi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1i.&quot;</em></div>\r\n<div><em><br>\r\n&quot;Man City kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng m\u00e3i, r\u1ed3i h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng v\u1eady th\u00f4i, cho n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadp trung cho ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, thay v\u00ec c\u1ee9 ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ecd. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ed9t, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.&quot;</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-liverpool-vs-fulham-172-202068.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/12/143729-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-liverpool-vs-fulham-172-202068.html\">Liverpool h\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p Fulham: Jurgen Klopp v\u00e0 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m&hellip; ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eddi</span><br>\r\nSau c\u00fa ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u1edf Champions League, The Kop c\u1ea7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng g\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1eady tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngay cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)&nbsp;</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"9380","checkdouble":"202184"},{"date":"16:23 13/11","title":"HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/25/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-mua-bang-duoc-nabil-fekir.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Nabil Fekir c\u1ee7a Lyon v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019, theo The Sun, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n The Blues \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Sarri v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, song h\u1ecd v\u1eabn g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Everton, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi BATE \u1edf Europa League nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1-0.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Nabil Fekir v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Nabil Fekir v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/12/Chelsea-muon-mua-Nabil-Fekir-vao-thang-1-nam-2019-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Maurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Chelsea l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata v\u00e0 Giroud tr\u1eadn n\u1ed5 tr\u1eadn x\u1ecbt, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Willian hay Pedro c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng n\u1ed5 s\u00fang \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n. Chelsea \u0111ang ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Eden Hazard.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, HLV Sarri \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Pedro v\u00e0 Willian \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nChelsea quan t\u00e2m Fekir</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Nabil Fekir c\u1ee7a Lyon v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019, theo The Sun, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n The Blues \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/30/HLV-Sarri-muon-Chelsea-mua-bang-duoc-sao-tuyen-Phap-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Nabil Fekir\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNabil Fekir \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Lyon, m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc anh ghi t\u1edbi 24 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 10 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Ligue 1 v\u00e0 Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng, ngo\u00e0i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh anh c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng hay trung phong \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nabil-fekir-bat-den-xanh-cho-chelsea-va-bayern-munich-172-201731.html\" target=\"_blank\"><em><u>Nabil Fekir t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Lyon</u></em></span>, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi ra \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Lyon, ngo\u00e0i The Blues th\u00ec Bayern Munich c\u0169ng \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"9379","checkdouble":"202186"},{"date":"17:44 13/11","title":"Andreas Christensen kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea nh\u01b0ng...","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/18/andreas-christensen-thua-nhan-khong-hai-long-voi-hlv-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Andreas Christensen n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Chelsea v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019.</h2><h2>Andreas Christensen kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Andreas Christensen l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Conte trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andreas Christensen n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Andreas Christensen n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Andreas-Christensen-noi-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andreas Christensen kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n. HLV Sarri s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng David Luiz v\u00e0 Rudiger \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, khi m\u1ed9t trong hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n Gary Cahill m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Andreas Christensen ch\u01b0a ra s\u00e2n m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat n\u00e0o \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00fap. Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean khi\u1ebfn Christensen ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng anh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nChristensen l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAndreas Christensen n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Chelsea v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andreas Christensen\" title=\"Andreas Christensen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/18/andreas-christensen-thua-nhan-khong-hai-long-voi-hlv-sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andreas Christensen l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean n\u1eefa\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 22 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf v\u1edbi HLV r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Chelsea v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-phu-phang-voi-christensen-172-199979.html\" target=\"_blank\"><em><u>HLV Maurizio Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Andreas Christensen</u></em></span>, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ebfu anh quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Chelsea \u00f4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"9378","checkdouble":"202187"},{"date":"17:16 13/11","title":"Si\u00eau th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/11/13/thu-mon-alisson-nhan-xet-ve-phong-do.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Liverpool. Anh th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, nh\u01b0ng \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o t\u1ea1i CLB m\u1edbi.</h2><h2><br>\r\nAlisson \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Liverpool b\u1ecf t\u1edbi 72.5 tri\u1ec7u euro (65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 Alisson t\u1eeb AS Roma. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb Chelsea ph\u00e1 v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Kepa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool mang theo nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc anh, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Simon Mignolet v\u00e0 Loris Karius khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/thu-mon-alisson-nhan-xet-ve-phong-do.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAnh th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra su\u00f4n s\u1ebb nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i. \u201c<em>Nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u1edf m\u1ee9c v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i</em>\u201d, Alisson n\u00f3i. \u201c<em>Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao d\u1ef1a theo ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>\u00c1p l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t cao v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i tr\u1edf n\u00ean ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i li\u1ec7u t\u00f4i c\u00f3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng hay kh\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m song t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n trong ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, thay \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1, gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. T\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool v\u00e0 \u0110T Brazil ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-liverpool-vs-fulham-172-202068.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/12/143729-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-liverpool-vs-fulham-172-202068.html\">Liverpool h\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p Fulham: Jurgen Klopp v\u00e0 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m\u2026 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eddi</span><br>\r\n<span>Sau c\u00fa ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u1edf Champions League, The Kop c\u1ea7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng g\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1eady tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngay cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-20-fulham-mai-nha-anfield-nang-buoc-lu-doan-do-172-202044.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/12/liverpool-20-fulham-mai-nha-anfield-nang-buoc-lu-doan-do.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-20-fulham-mai-nha-anfield-nang-buoc-lu-doan-do-172-202044.html\">Liverpool 2-0 Fulham: M\u00e1i nh\u00e0 Anfield n\u00e2ng b\u01b0\u1edbc L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Liverpool 2-0 Fulham ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Champions League h\u1ed3i gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n. Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n, s\u00e2n nh\u00e0...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-20-fulham-chien-thang-cua-nhung-nguoi-hung-tham-lang-172-202033.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/11/liverpool-20-fulham-chien-thang-cua-nhung-nguoi-hung-tham-lang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-20-fulham-chien-thang-cua-nhung-nguoi-hung-tham-lang-172-202033.html\">Liverpool 2-0 Fulham: Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng th\u1ea7m l\u1eb7ng</span><br>\r\n<span>Mohamed Salah l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n, nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng khen nh\u1ea5t sau d\u01b0 \u00e2m Liverpool vs Fulham, m\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"9377","checkdouble":"202192"}]}
