{"data":[{"date":"18:20 26/07","title":"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 1-1 AC Milan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/26/5-diem-nhan-sau-tran-dau-mu-11-ac-milan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sanchez l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Suso c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a ch\u1ec9 \u00edt ph\u00fat sau. T\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Man United l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c sau lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat penalty. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Sanchez ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 1-1 AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 1-1 AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sanchez t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Martial r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi tour du \u0111\u1ea5u M\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a Man United, HLV Jose Mourinho coi nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 n\u00e0o tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Lukaku v\u00e0 Rashford \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 sau khi \u0111i t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft b\u00e0i to\u00e1n nan gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Sanchez trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm. V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u1edf ph\u00fat 12 khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a Mata.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSanchez l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/video-tong-hop-mu-11-pen-98-ac-milan-icc-2018-329-192065.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU 1-1 AC&nbsp;Milan</span>. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho AC Milan v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng di chuy\u1ec3n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i sau 9 n\u0103m, Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f3 tin.</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a MU b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hang thu MU\" title=\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 MU b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 th\u1ee7ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Milan. Nh\u01b0ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 15 khi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Axel Tuanzebe \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed5ng Suso trong khi Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Chris Smalling thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 l\u01a1 l\u00e0 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Milan tho\u00e1t b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Man United c\u0169ng qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi n\u00e0y. Suso th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd b\u00f3ng n\u1ea3y m\u1ed9t nh\u1ecbp tr\u01b0\u1edbc tung c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00e1i ph\u00e1 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Lee Grant.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ef1c t\u1ee9c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y. Ngay sau khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 quay sang khu v\u1ef1c hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1eed ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 gi\u1eadn d\u1eef. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Mourinho s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<h2>Darmian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri \u00e2n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Darmian\" title=\"Darmian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/181449-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Darmian n\u1eafm gi\u1eef b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Antonio Valencia b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Mourinho bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1c \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a MU. Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra khi Darmian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e3nh tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch n\u00e0y \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p AC Milan thay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u00e2m ni\u00ean kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Smalling hay Mata.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Man United l\u00e0 Valencia v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Darmian nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i cho \u0111\u1ebfn sau khi tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Milan, Darmian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e2ng cao nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i trong vai tr\u00f2 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi Darmian khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c k\u00e9m. N\u1ebfu gi\u1eef Darmian trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n Premier League, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Mourinho s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i xoay v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 4 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Shaw kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Mourinho\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shaw\" title=\"Shaw\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Shaw ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc AC&nbsp;Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Darmian, Luke Shaw nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. S\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i l\u00e0 Ashley Young \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i th\u00eam sau World Cup 2018. Marcos Rojo c\u0169ng v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong khi Daley Blind \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ajax.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nShaw \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho v\u1eabn \u0111ang gi\u1eef ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Luke Shaw, d\u00f9 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f4ng khai ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Shaw \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 74 ph\u00fat nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Shaw c\u00f2n l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Anh b\u1ecb thay ra sau m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t Mourinho. Sau \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111i th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nShaw v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c HLV Mourinho v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, Shaw g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Old Trafford sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU&nbsp;1-1 AC&nbsp;Milan:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/26/MU-1-1-Milan.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4672","checkdouble":"192085"},{"date":"18:17 26/07","title":"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng khi giao h\u1eefu, c\u1eb7p sao Tottenham \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201cth\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3ng\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/26/hlv-pochettino-phat-bieu-ve-llorente-va-lucas.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas. \u00d4ng h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng cho h\u1ecd c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf Premier League sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham m\u1edbi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19. H\u1ecd giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi AS Roma trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean International Champions Cup. B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i n\u00e0y, Spurs v\u1eafng 9 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Harry Kane v\u00e0 Dele Alli do \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia h\u1ea1n ngh\u1ec9 ph\u00e9p sau World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3, Tottenham v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p Roma 4-1. Trong \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Fernando Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas Moura l\u00e0 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/hlv-pochettino-phat-bieu-ve-llorente-va-lucas.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Pochettino ca ng\u1ee3i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Mauricio Pochettino r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m. \u00d4ng hy v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0y trong nh\u1eefng tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. &ldquo;M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 World Cup. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. C\u1ea3 Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas \u0111\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng. H\u1ecd \u0111ang t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i&rdquo;, HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pochettino\" title=\"Pochettino\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/14/Mauricio-Pochettino-thay-the-Antonio-Conte-dan-dat-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Llorente v\u00e0 Lucas v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 khen ng\u1ee3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng, Pochettino n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &ldquo;\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i theo c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i&rdquo;, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i sau h\u01a1n 10 th\u00e1ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 20 ng\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. S\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Tottenham tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-muon-tai-ngo-modric-172-191894.html\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-to-long-thuong-hai-tottenham-172-191867.html\">Klopp t\u1ecf l\u00f2ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ea1i Tottenham</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/harry-kane-noi-gi-khi-tottenham-quyet-dinh-dung-ngoai-ttcn-172-191864.html\">Harry Kane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Tottenham quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ee9ng ngo\u00e0i TTCN?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-viec-mu-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-alderweireld-172-191725.html\">Mourinho n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c MU chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alderweireld?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-muon-roi-crystal-palace-va-tin-vui-cho-tottenham-172-191673.html\">Sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh NHA b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4671","checkdouble":"192084"},{"date":"16:26 26/07","title":"L\u00e1 th\u01b0 c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Modric g\u1eedi \u0111\u00e1p c\u00f4 b\u00e9 5 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb ung th\u01b0","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/la-thu-cam-dong-cua-tien-ve-modric-gui-dap-co-be-5-tuoi-bi-ung-thu.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4670","checkdouble":"192078"},{"date":"16:28 26/07","title":"Martial b\u1ecf d\u1edf du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u0103m v\u1ee3 sinh con","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/23/martial-bo-do-du-dau-cua-mu-de-cham-vo-sinh-con.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Martial kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u00f4ng x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Martial c\u00f3 xin ph\u00e9p HLV Mourinho hay kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi n\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Los Angeles. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00ecnh 26 tu\u1ed5i Melanie Da Cruz l\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ebb sinh \u0111\u1ee9a con \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00f2ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9a con th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a Martial. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 con g\u00e1i hai tu\u1ed5i Peyton t\u1eeb cu\u1ed9c h\u00f4n nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi v\u1ee3 c\u0169 Samantha Jacquelinet.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Martial b\u1ecf d\u1edf du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a MU \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u0103m v\u1ee3 sinh con h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Martial b\u1ecf d\u1edf du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a MU \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u0103m v\u1ee3 sinh con h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Tien-dao-Martial-bo-do-du-dau-cua-MU-de-cham-vo-sinh-con-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Melanie Da Cruz v\u00e0 b\u1ee5ng b\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng cu\u1ed1i thai k\u1ef3. \u1ea2nh: NN.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng hai, ng\u00f4i sao truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf Ph\u00e1p Melanie Da Cruz chia s\u1ebb th\u00f4ng tin c\u00f4 mang thai v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef: \"\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1eadu b\u00e9\" \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean c\u00e1t. Ng\u00e0y 17/7, Melanie Da Cruz \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i c\u00f4 \u00f4m b\u1ee5ng b\u1ea7u \u0111i d\u1ea1o b\u00ean s\u00f4ng Seine, Paris. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c t\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Martial v\u00e0 Melanie Da Cruz t\u1eebng g\u00e2y \u1ed3n \u00e0o khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o MU l\u00e0 Samantha Jacquelinet l\u00e0m \u1ea7m \u0129 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n. C\u00f4 n\u00e0y t\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh gi\u1eadt ch\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 Martial l\u00e0 k\u1ebb l\u1eeba d\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Martial khi anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb HLV Mourinho x\u1ebfp d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 22 tu\u1ed5i v\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf World Cup 2018 - gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. MU mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y Martial t\u1edbi Juventus hay Dortmund - nh\u1eefng CLB mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu anh. Martial ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4669","checkdouble":"192079"},{"date":"12:19 26/07","title":"B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/22/bui-tien-dung-va-nhung-cau-thu-u23-co-nguy-co-phai-ngoi-du-bi-tai-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong th\u1eddi gian qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>1. B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a NHM.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 m\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u1eeba qua tu\u1ed5i 20 nh\u01b0 Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn. H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 \u01b0u \u00e1i t\u1eeb HLV Marian Mihail, tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi v\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia tay Thanh H\u00f3a, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Bui-Tien-Dung-va-nhung-cau-thu-co-the-phai-ngoi-du-bi-tai-ASIAD-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh sau VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i FLC Thanh H\u00f3a thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Tr\u1ea7n B\u1eedu Ng\u1ecdc. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c v\u00f2ng 18 v\u00e0 19, B\u1eedu Ng\u1ecdc c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng cho v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 tr\u1eadn thua 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap QG v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng, ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0o tay &lsquo;\u0111\u00e0n anh&rsquo; V\u0103n L\u00e2m, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y t\u1ea1i H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bui-tien-dung-phoi-bay-nhieu-van-de-sau-tran-thua-cua-flc-thanh-hoa-168-192028.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/Bui-Tien-Dung-va-nhung-cau-thu-co-the-phai-ngoi-du-bi-tai-ASIAD-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bui-tien-dung-phoi-bay-nhieu-van-de-sau-tran-thua-cua-flc-thanh-hoa-168-192028.html\">B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ph\u01a1i b\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng sau tr\u1eadn thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 SLNA chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 25/7.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. Ph\u1ea1m \u0110\u1ee9c Huy<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ee9c Huy ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 &lsquo;m\u00e1y qu\u00e9t&rsquo; c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, bao qu\u00e1t v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 cho Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 5-4-1 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9, \u0110\u1ee9c Huy \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c ti\u00eau ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111eo b\u00e1m, tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh b\u00f3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c Huy c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U21 Viet Nam tien ve Duc Huy\" title=\"U21 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ee9c Huy\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/12/14/U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Myanmar-Dau-se-la-cua-de-danh-cua-ong-Park-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ee9c Huy c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0o tay Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Moses thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110\u1ee9c Huy d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u00e0 Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho HAGL, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0110\u1ee9c Huy ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ea1i CLB SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o qu\u00ea Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 cho m\u00ecnh 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i V-League v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai trong danh s\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i binh ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c &ldquo;tung ho\u00e0nh&rdquo; khi b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ASIAD. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t t\u1eeb C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Ti\u1ebfn Linh, V\u0103n To\u00e0n ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 c\u00e1c &lsquo;l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng&rsquo; V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i an ph\u1eadn d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Duc Chinh la diem sang hiem hoi trong so cac ngoi sao tan cong U23 Viet Nam\" title=\"\u0110\u1ee9c Chinh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng hi\u1ebfm hoi trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/Duc-Chinh-nhan-giai-ban-thang-dep-nhat-V-League-thang-4--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ee9c Chinh (tr\u00e1i) c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh c\u00f2n b\u1ecb t\u0103ng c\u00e2n, v\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y nhanh ch\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea3i kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. Song \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng khi m\u00e0 ASIAD \u0111ang t\u1edbi r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>4. Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao n\u1eefa c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ch\u1ecbu s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y t\u1eadp trung V-League, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 anh c\u0169ng v\u1eeba m\u1edbi b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tran Dinh Trong van ra san tap luyen cung cac dong doi du chan thuong chua binh phuc hoan toan.\" title=\"Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng v\u1eabn ra s\u00e2n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i d\u00f9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u01b0a b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/IMG_0592_resize.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1997. L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 ngo\u00e0i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a Th\u00e0nh Chung, Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t t\u00e2n binh h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i. V\u00ec th\u1ebf n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9, nguy c\u01a1 \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra.</p>\r\n<h2>5. V\u0169 V\u0103n Thanh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean, V\u0103n Thanh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, s\u1ef1 kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ng\u00f4i sao HAGL lu\u00f4n d\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c c\u00f9ng U23 VN, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Thanh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ecdng. D\u00f9 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i HAGL v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 19/20 tr\u1eadn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai song V\u0103n Thanh v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vu Van Thanh\" title=\"V\u0169 V\u0103n Thanh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/12/bau-duc-giai-thich-ly-do-khong-cho-van-thanh-sang-chau-au-thi-dau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0169 V\u0103n Thanh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 nh\u01b0 1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Thanh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y d\u00f9 anh v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t x\u00f4ng x\u00e1o v\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng HAGL.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, V\u0103n Thanh c\u0169ng \u0111ang ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. V\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0o tay Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 cao t\u1ea1i SLNA.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-lo-ngai-ve-kha-nang-tien-xa-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192032.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/chuyen-gia-lo-ngai-ve-kha-nang-tien-xa-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-lo-ngai-ve-kha-nang-tien-xa-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192032.html\">Chuy\u00ean gia lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 V\u0169 M\u1ea1nh H\u1ea3i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-mu-tit-ve-doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-168-192019.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/24/hlv-park-hang-seo-mu-tit-ve-doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-mu-tit-ve-doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-168-192019.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo m\u00f9 t\u1ecbt v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1eafp ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout-168-192005.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout-168-192005.html\">ASIAD 2018: Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ec5 qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, kh\u00f3 th\u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out</span><br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a 26 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;color:#222222\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4668","checkdouble":"192063"},{"date":"12:35 26/07","title":"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/cong-phuong-tu-tin-se-co-suat-da-chinh-tai-asiad-2018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng s\u00e1ng 26/7, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n anh \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e1ng 26/7, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp ri\u00eang do d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd s\u1edbm l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/photo1532572724216-15325727242161016033701.png\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i: \"Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a em \u0111\u00e3 \u1ed5n v\u00e0 em \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. L\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung n\u00e0y t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ee7a em c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Em ngh\u0129 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed7i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 ngang nhau n\u00ean em v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng. C\u00e1c anh l\u1edbn ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh th\u00ec n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c m\u1edbi \u0111i l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, n\u00ean em kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p b\u1ed5 sung c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do v\u00ec sao c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t. V\u00e0 d\u0129 nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \"Em ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o trong b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh. Em v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u nay, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra s\u00e2n luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp t\u1eeb 16h00. Bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t t\u1eeb 4 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 SLNA v\u00ec b\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 25/7.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bui-tien-dung-va-nhung-cau-thu-u23-co-nguy-co-phai-ngoi-du-bi-tai-asiad-2018-168-192063.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/22/bui-tien-dung-va-nhung-cau-thu-u23-co-nguy-co-phai-ngoi-du-bi-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bui-tien-dung-va-nhung-cau-thu-u23-co-nguy-co-phai-ngoi-du-bi-tai-asiad-2018-168-192063.html\">B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong th\u1eddi gian qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4667","checkdouble":"192064"},{"date":"13:20 26/07","title":"B\u00e1c s\u0129 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/bac-si-noi-gi-ve-chan-thuong-cua-cong-phuong-xuan-manh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, b\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng n\u00ean 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa.</h2><h2>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00e1c s\u0129 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00e1c s\u0129 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/cong-phuong-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd s\u1edbm b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c do ch\u1ec9 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn 3 ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa SLNA v\u00e0 HAGL cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c truy c\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Sau khi ki\u1ec3m tra, c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129 k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh b\u1ecb l\u1eadt c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00ea Y\u00ean Th\u00e0nh, Ngh\u1ec7 An kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i C\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c Gia 2018 gi\u1eefa FLC Thanh H\u00f3a vs SLNA. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf Trung t\u00e2m PVF t\u1ea1i H\u01b0ng Y\u00ean trong ng\u00e0y 25/7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb d\u00e3n d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1c s\u0129 Tr\u1ea7n Anh Tu\u1ea5n chia s\u1ebb: \u201cC\u00e1c em n\u00f3 ch\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn mai l\u00e0 t\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00f4i, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e2u v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng nh\u1eb9 th\u00f4i m\u00e0. C\u00f2n ri\u00eang C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00ec h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ed3i\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 vui h\u01a1n v\u1edbi HLV Park Hang Seo. Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n \u1edf Trung t\u00e2m PVF t\u1eeb nay cho \u0111\u1ebfn 31/8. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 1/8, \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 H\u00f9ng di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u1eb7p Palestine (3/8), Oman (5/8) v\u00e0 Uzbekistan (7/8). \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bui-tien-dung-va-nhung-cau-thu-u23-co-nguy-co-phai-ngoi-du-bi-tai-asiad-2018-168-192063.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/22/bui-tien-dung-va-nhung-cau-thu-u23-co-nguy-co-phai-ngoi-du-bi-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bui-tien-dung-va-nhung-cau-thu-u23-co-nguy-co-phai-ngoi-du-bi-tai-asiad-2018-168-192063.html\">B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong th\u1eddi gian qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-tu-tin-se-co-suat-da-chinh-tai-asiad-2018-168-192064.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/cong-phuong-tu-tin-se-co-suat-da-chinh-tai-asiad-2018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-tu-tin-se-co-suat-da-chinh-tai-asiad-2018-168-192064.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng s\u00e1ng 26/7, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n anh \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4666","checkdouble":"192066"},{"date":"17:01 26/07","title":"\u0110\u00e1 th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a sau","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/26/da-tho-bao-sam-ngoc-duc-nhan-an-phat-cam-thi-dau-den-ca-mua-sau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00e1 th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng t\u1eeb Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a sau.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa CLB TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng. Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh r\u00fat th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf v\u1edbi S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c, c\u00f2n Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t may kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sam Ngoc Duc nhan an phat cam thi dau den 8 tran.\" title=\"S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn 8 tr\u1eadn.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/da-tho-bao-sam-ngoc-duc-nhan-an-phat-cam-thi-dau-den-ca-mua-sau.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn 8 tr\u1eadn.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nSau v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c, Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00f3m h\u1ecdp v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t v\u1edbi S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a CLB TP.HCM b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u 8 tr\u1eadn, ph\u1ea1t 35 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00ec c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi &quot;c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh x\u00e2m ph\u1ea1m th\u00e2n th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c V-League 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 6 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00f9a. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a sau v\u00ec \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 8 tr\u1eadn khi c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i khi ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Anh H\u00f9ng (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng). M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed1c Ngh\u1ec7 An c\u0169ng t\u1eebng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e0n em \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n SLNA t\u1ea1i C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i \u0111\u00f3, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 4 tr\u1eadn. T\u00ednh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 6 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, 2 th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf. \u00d4ng Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1ea3i H\u01b0\u1eddng, tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c r\u0103n \u0111e b\u1edfi S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i nguy hi\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nan-nhan-cua-sam-ngoc-duc-mong-muon-dieu-nay-sau-cu-dap-troi-giang-168-191901.html\">N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p tr\u1eddi gi\u00e1ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-nhieu-lan-roi-291-191892.html\">S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-168-191885.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao-168-191820.html\">HLV Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/clb-tphcm-keu-troi-vi-luc-luong-sam-ngoc-duc-duoc-giam-an-treo-gio-291-187003.html\">CLB TP.HCM k\u00eau tr\u1eddi v\u00ec l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/sau-khi-cong-vinh-tu-chuc-thay-tro-hlv-miura-nhan-them-tin-du-291-185533.html\">Sau khi C\u00f4ng Vinh t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Miura nh\u1eadn th\u00eam tin d\u1eef</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4665","checkdouble":"192077"},{"date":"14:18 26/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Atletico Madrid vs Arsenal 18h35 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/nhan-dinh-atletico-madrid-vs-arsenal-18h35-ngay-267-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Atletico Madrid vs Arsenal l\u00fac 18h35 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Atletico Madrid vs Arsenal 18h35 ng\u00e0y 267 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Atletico Madrid vs Arsenal 18h35 ng\u00e0y 267 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2672018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Atletico Madrid vs Arsenal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>Atletico Madrid vs Arsenal: 1-4<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ICC 2018 g\u1eb7p Arsenal m\u1edbi l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Diego Simeone trong m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay. S\u1edf d\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Madrid c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ch\u1eadm tr\u1ec5 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 do \u0111a s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang ngh\u1ec9 ph\u00e9p sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac VCK World Cup 2018. G\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i nay, Atletico s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi qu\u00e1 n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, Atletico s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Antoine Griezmann v\u00e0 Diego Costa. \u1ede tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Koke, Saul Niguez v\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh Thomas Lemar. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf h\u00e0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, HLV Simeone kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc g\u1ed3m Diego Godin, Sime Vrsaljko, Filipe Luis v\u00e0 Jose Gimenez. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal t\u1ed1i nay \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u00f4ng Simeone ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u00e0n th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u00e1c \u201cbinh nh\u00ec\u201d. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Aletico n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u1edbi trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup, s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng Jan Oblak gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eb9n nguy\u00ean m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Arsenal. Xin nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng, \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f9i d\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Boreham Wood t\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1, trong \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang l\u1eadp 1 hat-trick.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Atletico l\u00e0 Aubameyang v\u00e0 Alexandre Lacazette. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Boreham Wood, \u201csong s\u00e1t\u201d n\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0103n \u00fd. Trong \u0111\u00f3, Aubameyang \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Boreham Wood. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng Mesut Oezil \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Arsenal ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nghi\u1ec1n n\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Atletico b\u1eaft ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1 sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn. Do v\u1eady, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i nay c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London tr\u1ea3 h\u1eadn. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Arsenal thay HLV l\u00e3o l\u00e0ng Arsene Wenger.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n5 - L\u00e0 s\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh m\u00e0 Arsenal mang \u0111\u1ebfn Sigapore \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 ICC. H\u1ecd g\u1ed3m Bernd Leno, Sokratis, Matteo Guendouzi, Emile Smith Rowe v\u00e0 Eddie Nketiah. Ri\u00eang t\u00e2n binh Lucas Torreira ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 8 m\u1edbi h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN XUNG QUANH<br>\r\n- Theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Atletico th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 1/2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y g\u1eb7p Arsenal. <br>\r\n- Theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Atletico th\u1eafng 5, thua 2/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. <br>\r\n- Theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Arsenal th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 2, thua 2/8 tr\u1eadn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n- 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Atletico c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean trong hi\u1ec7p 1. C\u1ea3 6 tr\u1eadn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nL\u1ebb b\u00e0n th\u1eafng<br>\r\n2/3 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i k\u1ebft th\u00fac l\u1ebb b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. 5/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Atletico c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ebb. 4/6 tr\u1eadn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Arsenal c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chia h\u1ebft cho 2. Do v\u1eady, tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac l\u1ebb b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4664","checkdouble":"192068"},{"date":"15:24 26/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Atletico Madrid vs Arsenal 18h35 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/26/atletico-madrid-vs-arsenal-tran-dau-icc-2018-ngay-hom-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Atletico Madrid vs Arsenal: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal vs Atletico Madrid gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018 l\u00fac 18h35 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 26/7.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n5 - L\u00e0 s\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh m\u00e0 Arsenal mang \u0111\u1ebfn Sigapore \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 ICC. H\u1ecd g\u1ed3m Bernd Leno, Sokratis, Matteo Guendouzi, Emile Smith Rowe v\u00e0 Eddie Nketiah. Ri\u00eang t\u00e2n binh Lucas Torreira ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 8 m\u1edbi h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Arsenal.<br>\r\n<h2>TH\u00d4NG TIN XUNG QUANH</h2>\r\n- Theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Atletico th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 1/2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y g\u1eb7p Arsenal. <br>\r\n- Theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Atletico th\u1eafng 5, thua 2/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. <br>\r\n- Theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Arsenal th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 2, thua 2/8 tr\u1eadn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n- 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Atletico c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean trong hi\u1ec7p 1. C\u1ea3 6 tr\u1eadn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T</h2>\r\nL\u1ebb b\u00e0n th\u1eafng<br>\r\n2/3 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i k\u1ebft th\u00fac l\u1ebb b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. 5/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Atletico c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ebb. 4/6 tr\u1eadn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Arsenal c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chia h\u1ebft cho 2. Do v\u1eady, tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac l\u1ebb b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nAtletico Madrid: Oblak \u2013 Juanfran, Montero, Rodriguez, Solano \u2013 Garcia, Olabe, Partey, Vitolo \u2013 Vietto, Gameiro<br>\r\nArsenal: Leno \u2013 Bellerin, Mustafi, Sokratis, Kolasinac \u2013 Ramsey, Elneny \u2013 Mkhitaryan, Ozil, Aubameyang \u2013 Lacazette\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/14/Boreham-Wood-vs-Arsenal_mp4_Output_1.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4663","checkdouble":"192074"},{"date":"15:52 26/07","title":"Mourinho \u0111e d\u1ecda Liverpool v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec3m h\u1ecda m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/mourinho-de-doa-liverpool-ve-hiem-hoa-mua-bong-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, HLV Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Klopp bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a Liverpool \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMourinho ghen t\u1ef5 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111em v\u1ec1 4 t\u00e2n binh kh\u1ee7ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y tham v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf, \u0111i\u1ec1u M.U ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111em nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o Jurgen Klopp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Mourinho cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0, t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1ebft l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n n\u00ean c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh trong ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. M\u1ecdi t\u00e2n binh Liverpool \u0111em v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u00f4i m\u1eebng cho h\u1ecd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, s\u1ebd l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi b\u1ea1n y\u00eau c\u1ea7u h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi ti\u00eau. H\u1ecd ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng gi\u00eang v\u1edbi Virgil Van Dijk, \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Klopp v\u1ec1 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\" title=\"Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Klopp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/mourinho-de-doa-liverpool-ve-hiem-hoa-mua-bong-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Klopp v\u1ec1 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nQuay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, Mourinho chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng: &ldquo;V\u00e2ng, Darmian \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. V\u00e0 khi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ebfu CLB nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ecf ra nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i ra \u0111i b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho Darmian l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Valencia \u0111ang ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, Dalot c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Young v\u00e0 Lindelof c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, Darmian ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. B\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qua nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Klopp bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 ghen t\u1ef5 khi \u00f4ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/smalling-khong-dem-xia-den-viec-mu-mua-them-trung-ve-172-192073.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/23/smalling-khong-dem-xia-den-viec-mu-mua-them-trung-ve.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/smalling-khong-dem-xia-den-viec-mu-mua-them-trung-ve-172-192073.html\">Smalling kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfm x\u1ec9a \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c M.U mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n xung quanh vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, trung v\u1ec7 Smalling s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Man United.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-giuc-mu-mua-maguire-172-192058.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/mourinho-giuc-mu-mua-maguire.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-giuc-mu-mua-maguire-172-192058.html\">Mourinho gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U mua g\u1ea5p sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span><br>\r\nMourinho gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U mua Maguire. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4662","checkdouble":"192071"},{"date":"15:57 26/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! Ng\u00f4i sao ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda r\u1eddi M.U nh\u1ea5t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/mourinh-xac-nhan-darmian-co-the-roi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Darmian mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 Antonio Valencia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDarmian mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Matteo Darmian r\u1eddi Man United kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd m\u1edbi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb ph\u00eda CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u01a1i cho Juventus. 1 n\u0103m tr\u00f4i qua, \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh HLV Jose Mourinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Darmian \u0111\u00e3 mang b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi AC Milan t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup. Anh ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m. Chung cu\u1ed9c, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Milan 9-9 \u1edf ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n sau khi h\u00f2a 1-1 \u1edf 2 hi\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Darmian mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Darmian mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/mourinh-xac-nhan-darmian-co-the-roi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Darmian \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Milan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn, Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Darmian mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U. \u201cB\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Darmian b\u1edfi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi trong 2 n\u0103m t\u00f4i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi 1 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Van Gaal. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u00e0ng trai lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh c\u00f3, tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb AC Milan v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi CLB th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cG\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i CLB c\u0169 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu mang nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a. Darmian mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 khi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u01b0 x\u1eed c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDarmian \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Juventus v\u00e0 Inter Milan li\u00ean h\u1ec7 nh\u01b0ng Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 M.U ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam vi\u1ec7c Antonio Valencia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Darmian ra \u0111i v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho\" title=\"HLV Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/HLV-Mourinho-cua-M.U.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Darmian mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCho \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho Darmian ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u01b0ng \u00fd\u201d, Mourinho n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cValencia \u0111ang ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Diogo Dalot c\u0169ng v\u1eady. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Ashley Young c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang \u0111\u00e1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a M.U khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. \u00d4ng s\u1ebd y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1eadu World Cup 2018 khi c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cAshley Young c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i song \u0111ang \u0111i ngh\u1ec9. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00ec t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n nay hay ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8. Victor Lindelof c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u00f9 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 2 t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Manchester\u201d, Mourinho ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u00ec v\u1eady, Darmian s\u1ebd ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u00edch h\u1ee3p g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/smalling-khong-dem-xia-den-viec-mu-mua-them-trung-ve-172-192073.html\">Smalling kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfm x\u1ec9a \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c M.U mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-giuc-mu-mua-maguire-172-192058.html\">Mourinho gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U mua g\u1ea5p sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-mu-cam-thay-hanh-phuc-khi-co-hlv-moi-172-192053.html\">Sao M.U c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi c\u00f3 HLV m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-mu-va-real-tu-choi-mua-malcom-180-192001.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: MU v\u00e0 Real t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua Malcom</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-bailey-thay-willian-172-191982.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean Chelsea s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Willian cho M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4661","checkdouble":"192072"},{"date":"15:15 26/07","title":"Smalling kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfm x\u1ec9a \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c M.U mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/23/smalling-khong-dem-xia-den-viec-mu-mua-them-trung-ve.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n xung quanh vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, trung v\u1ec7 Smalling s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Man United.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nSmalling kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i t\u00e2n binh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh, t\u1eeb gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. M\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7. V\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Old Trafford, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, Chris Smalling v\u00e0 Eric Bailly \u0111ang ch\u01a1i trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, trong khi b\u1ed9 ba Jones &ndash; Lindelof &ndash; Rojo \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018. C\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh cho r\u1eb1ng, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina Marcos Rojo \u0111ang lo ng\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n, Chris Smalling l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;C\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady h\u00e0ng n\u0103m. CLB n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c nhau, d\u00f9 l\u00e0 h\u1ecfi mua th\u1eadt hay tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u00f4 c\u0103n c\u1ee9, r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Smalling s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i M.U\" title=\"Smalling vs Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/23/smalling-khong-dem-xia-den-viec-mu-mua-them-trung-ve.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Smalling s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 lo l\u1eafng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec, t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i M.U v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u quen thu\u1ed9c trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua, gi\u1eef chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t&rdquo; &ndash; Chris Smalling t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup: &ldquo;R\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, b\u1edfi v\u00ec b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. D\u00f9 sao, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Smalling s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. B\u1edfi cho d\u00f9 c\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng bom t\u1ea5n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1edf h\u1eefu tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-11-pen-98-ac-milan-icc-2018-329-192065.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/video-tong-hop-mu-11-pen-98-ac-milan-icc-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-11-pen-98-ac-milan-icc-2018-329-192065.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 1-1 (pen 9-8) AC Milan (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 s\u1edbm do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez nh\u01b0ng Man Utd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 sau 90 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Milan v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i sau \u0111\u1ebfn 13 l\u01b0\u1ee3t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-giuc-mu-mua-maguire-172-192058.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/mourinho-giuc-mu-mua-maguire.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-giuc-mu-mua-maguire-172-192058.html\">Mourinho gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U mua g\u1ea5p sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span><br>\r\nMourinho gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U mua Maguire. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4660","checkdouble":"192073"}]}
